{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5a5dab73bd","title":"对北京市防疫工作会议情况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7422629686","index":0,"year":1952,"month":4,"day":9,"articleId":"5a5dab73bd"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"5610a9f8cf","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5a5dab73bd","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"贺，指贺诚，当时任中央人民政府卫生部副部长、人民革命军事委员会卫生部部长。傅，指博连障，当时任人民革命军事委员会卫生部副部长。"},{"id":"af1e946201","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5a5dab73bd","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭真，当时任中共北京市委书记、北京市人民政府市长。"},{"id":"09198bbf71","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5a5dab73bd","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指贺诚、傅连障1952年4月7日关于北京市防疫工作会议给毛泽东的报告。报告汇报了北京市、中央和军委直属单位的防疫情况及会议决定的几个问题，并提出了以下几个请示解决的问题：一、建议北京市召开一次各界人民代表会议，对防疫工作再作一次动员。二、为改善环境卫生，拟将全市污水沟的12处明沟改为暗沟，修整陶然亭污水笔池为游览湖池，施工预算为500亿元，望中央批准拨专款解决。三、为防止急性传染病蔓延，建议北京市建一所拥有200个床位的隔离病院。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8cc64739d5","type":"title","text":"对北京市防疫工作会议情况报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5a5dab73bd"},{"id":"5610a9f8cf","type":"paragraph","text":"贺、傅二同志阅后，送彭真同志周总理的办","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5a5dab73bd"},{"id":"af1e946201","type":"paragraph","text":"我认为拨五百亿元办理本件所讲的卫生工程，并建一隔离病完是必要的，是否可行，请周召集一次会议予以决定","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5a5dab73bd"},{"id":"09198bbf71","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5a5dab73bd"},{"id":"2248250240","type":"paragraph","text":"四月九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5a5dab73bd"}],"page":{"id":"f5619b8329","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5a5dab73bd","start":55,"end":55}}}},"__N_SSG":true}